premise_source_doc_sentence: As a result of the war the State of Israel retained the area that the UN General Assembly Resolution 181 had recommended for the proposed Jewish state as well as almost 60 % of the area of Arab state proposed by the 1948 Partition Plan , including the Jaffa , Lydda and Ramle area , Galilee , some parts of the Negev , a wide strip along the Tel-Aviv-Jerusalem road , West Jerusalem , and some territories in the West Bank .
The `` Jewish state '' is a political term used to describe the nation state of Israel .
